{"tid":2052512,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有個日本朋友問我點解香港人要救自由 我應該點答佢","createTime":"2020-06-05T14:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T15:48:25.000Z","uid":172497,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b21d0f501631fe33f84b3382f24fd1432abe3c5d","tid":2052512,"uid":172497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T14:51:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6s5zJ55.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6s5zJ55.png&h=cc1da700&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n識日文既可以自己去佢fb同佢傾下<br />\n等日本人了解我地多d"},{"pid":"c24d07f0c4f0e9085690ad97e5c110b16d9125e5","tid":2052512,"uid":279321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T15:15:20.000Z","msg":"阿鬼你不如講返日文"},{"pid":"c2350d7f0001af15e5818f2d0a7c42fff95bfa63","tid":2052512,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T03:58:39.000Z","msg":"如果去風俗店嘅自由都冇嘅地方你會唔會留喺度"},{"pid":"9df76ff4eadddd27adc85768b3e75f1e280dae79","tid":2052512,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:07:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ErkinSidick/status/1257168607584247809?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FErkinSidick%2Fstatus%2F1257168607584247809%3Fs%3D20&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGcFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=7d7ba97d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FErkinSidick%2Fstatus%2F1257168607584247809%3Fs%3D20&h=35bc0b90\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ErkinSidick/status/1257168607584247809?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/AbdugheniSabit/status/1267011567071133699?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAbdugheniSabit%2Fstatus%2F1267011567071133699%3Fs%3D20&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGcFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=5f718c10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAbdugheniSabit%2Fstatus%2F1267011567071133699%3Fs%3D20&h=d4c1df95\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/AbdugheniSabit/status/1267011567071133699?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n維族再教育營, 除了非法關押及勞改思想不跟黨走的人<br />\n還有漢人強逼維族嫁給他們, 由於鼓勵壯維族與漢人結婚的政策, 政府基本上對這些逼婚行為閉一隻眼, 甚至有官員用職權之利參與其中<br />\n<br />\n有傳言, 有個案是把丈夫鎖到營中, 威脅人妻嫁給他, 否則丈夫會很慘, 關到死<br />\n<br />\n又有很多故事是維族與外國人結婚, 拿了外國護照, 居住權, 被中國用身在中國的家人威脅要回來, 要帶小孩上中國學校, 否則家人有難等等<br />\n簡單來講要將整個維族轉化成愛國中國人, 一點一滴維族的人力都要拿盡"},{"pid":"cebe0d1db1774893f094e0d9a352ed34a69f70d1","tid":2052512,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:12:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/kasehsaulmouk/status/1206468736753864704?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkasehsaulmouk%2Fstatus%2F1206468736753864704%3Fs%3D20&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGcFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=4665590f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkasehsaulmouk%2Fstatus%2F1206468736753864704%3Fs%3D20&h=58bbf42e\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/kasehsaulmouk/status/1206468736753864704?s=20</a><br />\n被關押的人常在抖音上載哭泣的影片, 偶爾貼個被關押家人的照片, 在影片中與他互動, 希望外界知道能援助, 可惜, 遠到香港已經沒幾個人知道, 還一堆人認為是偽造, 胡說, 香港以後也只能這樣示威, 拍個哭哭影片就當自已示威<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/arslan_hidayat/status/1198179073811525632?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Farslan_hidayat%2Fstatus%2F1198179073811525632%3Fs%3D20&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGcFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=2371e29e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Farslan_hidayat%2Fstatus%2F1198179073811525632%3Fs%3D20&h=70f24f63\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/arslan_hidayat/status/1198179073811525632?s=20</a><br />\n這個是心很痛的意思?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/arslan_hidayat/status/1184512382493696003?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Farslan_hidayat%2Fstatus%2F1184512382493696003%3Fs%3D20&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGcFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=545dbc17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Farslan_hidayat%2Fstatus%2F1184512382493696003%3Fs%3D20&h=f7150beb\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/arslan_hidayat/status/1184512382493696003?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/arslan_hidayat/status/1173975989564710912?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Farslan_hidayat%2Fstatus%2F1173975989564710912%3Fs%3D20&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGcFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=1f9016a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Farslan_hidayat%2Fstatus%2F1173975989564710912%3Fs%3D20&h=acefcbde\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/arslan_hidayat/status/1173975989564710912?s=20</a><br />\n這一定是造謠?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/arslan_hidayat/status/1163193299177545729?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Farslan_hidayat%2Fstatus%2F1163193299177545729%3Fs%3D20&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGcFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=01ab5773\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Farslan_hidayat%2Fstatus%2F1163193299177545729%3Fs%3D20&h=4229a8c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/arslan_hidayat/status/1163193299177545729?s=20</a><br />\n如果這條片是造謠, 我假的也信了"},{"pid":"cc7db2d16db8ec5a65db471a47d2214483e6c925","tid":2052512,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:19:43.000Z","msg":"很多中國人說: 香港已經很自由, 為什麼還需要自由?<br />\n<br />\n我的回答是: 很多身處中國 反顛覆政權罪底下的人, 因為做自已本應被世界允許的本質, 例如宗教, 公義, 法律, 甚至是財產權, 土地權, 或個人思想作品, 要面對不合理既法律, 終生坐牢, 侮辱, 恐嚇, 襲擊. 很多個案都顯示, 中國在執行這條所謂法律, 不一定會依法辦事, 只要能夠讓聲音滅絕, 違法是允許的. 這不是歷史上所傳承美妙文化的中國. 你願意你所生活的地方是這樣嗎?"},{"pid":"0a42ab85d9e784f13c6b9c1df80e3999a3f06736","tid":2052512,"uid":279357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T15:48:25.000Z","msg":"因為唔想似當年天皇咁<br />\n做錯決定帶人民走上絕路<br />\n戰時受傷嘅係本土日本平民<br />\n戰後日本後代背負上一代嘅錯<br />\n前人亂做決定後人要幾代去償還"}]}